@startuml init
!include ../_common.puml

' SkillIndexer is a Phase 2 deliverable; shown here for contract completeness (SPEC-02).
participant SkillIndexer as SI
note over SI: Phase 2 deliverable; shown for contract completeness

box "Init only" #FAFAFA
  participant SI
end box

== Server bootstrap ==

[-> SI : 1. main.py constructs SkillIndexer
SI -> SI : 2. walks skills/ for SKILL.md files\n   (filesystem scan)
SI -> SI : 3. parses YAML frontmatter\n   (python-frontmatter)
SI -> SI : 4. writes .skills-index/catalog.json
SI -> CAT : 5. returns Catalog (frozen) to main
note over CAT: In-memory Catalog is now frozen\n(no further disk I/O at call time)

[-> LM : 6a. main.py constructs LockManager (idle)
[-> TM : 6b. main.py constructs TaskManager(catalog, lock, runner, store)
[-> F  : 7. main.py registers @mcp.tool functions on FastMCP instance
F -->] : 8. FastMCP ready — listening on stdio/HTTP

@enduml
